title: As a U.S. aid ship heads to Gaza, Biden again warns Netanyahu on civilian deaths
description: The U.S. ship left Virginia this weekend as part of an emergency mission to build a temporary pier in Gaza to facilitate aid. Biden criticized the Israeli prime minister over civilian deaths in Gaza.

title: Readers' wishes for Ramadan: Cease-fire in Gaza, peace on Earth and more empathy
description: The holiest month in the Muslim calendar begins for many on Monday. This is what NPR readers will be praying for.
